13:03.583 --> 13:05.085
and you are gonna tell me why,

13:05.085 --> 13:08.088
and you will not be
able to hide from that.

13:08.088 --> 13:10.757
(ominous music)

13:12.159 --> 13:14.661
- My favorite part
of Frankenstein

13:14.661 --> 13:16.864
is that Mary Shelly was queer,

13:16.864 --> 13:20.333
because as many historians
love to argue against,

13:20.333 --> 13:25.338
we have written texts from Mary
Shelly to her friend saying

13:26.739 --> 13:28.942
that she likes to get
tousey-mousey with women.

13:28.942 --> 13:31.011
(somber string music)

13:31.011 --> 13:35.248
- "April 8th, 1825.

13:35.248 --> 13:36.950
